column1: Appendix table 10: Number of sentenced prisoners admitted into and released from state or federal jurisdiction, by jurisdiction, December 31, 2000, 2008, and 2009
Authors: Heather C. West, Ph.D., William J. Sabol, Ph.D., and Sarah J. Greenman
Appendix table 10. Number of sentenced prisoners admitted into and released from state or federal jurisdiction, by jurisdiction, December 31, 2000, 2008, and 2009
Note: Totals based on prisoners with a sentence of more than 1 year. Totals exclude escapees, AWOLS, and transfers to and from other jurisdictions. See Methodology.
